OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry but often cloudy.
OL,6,FHowever, some bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fwill occur, especially this morning
OL,8,Fonce any early patchy mist or fog
OL,9,Fclears. Very light winds. Slight
OL,10,Fmilder for most places compared to
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry and cloudy start, except
OL,14,Fperhaps some early clear spells across
OL,15,Feastern areas. Later this evening
OL,16,Fpatchy light rain arrives, and
OL,17,Fpersists overnight as hill fog
OL,18,Fdevelops.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
